        <updateDate>2010-10-27T19:13:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Home School Equity Act for Tax Relief of 2010 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) extend through 2010 the tax deduction for expenses of elementary and secondary school teachers; and (2) expand the definition of &quot;school&quot; for purposes of such tax deduction to include a home school.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
